type: wall

name: "Plated Plastanium Wall"
description: "Protects structures from enemy projectiles. Has more health and armor than the regular Plastanium Wall. Absorbs lasers and electric arcs. Blocks automatic power connections."
details: "Meowho! I am la Plastani-Chan~! Dont cal me Plastic! Mwa!"

health: 750
armor: 3

size: 1
buildTime: 19
